&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Calculation:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/23/02/F2_Engineering_Mrunal_23.02.2023_D2.png&quot; style=&quot;height: 147px; width: 200px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Here,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;AB = Height of the light-house from the sea level&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;BC = Distance between the foot of the light-house and the boat&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Angle of depression =&amp;nbsp;&amp;ang;DAC = 30&amp;deg;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Since, AD is parallel to BC,&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;ang;DAC = 30&amp;deg; =&amp;nbsp;&amp;ang;ACB&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;Delta;ABC is a right-angled triangle at B.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;So,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;tan 30&amp;deg; = AB/BC&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;rArr;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class=&quot;math-tex&quot;&gt;\(\frac {1}{\sqrt3}\)&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;=&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class=&quot;math-tex&quot;&gt;\(\frac {50}{BC}\)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

